After unpacking the tar file; as root:

	Execute the script ./vss-hv-driver-install to build and install
	Hyper-V backup components on a rhel5.x installation. Once the script completes,
	reboot the machine.

	To uninstall Hyper-V backup components, execute the script
	./vss-hv-driver-uninstall. Once the script completes, reboot the machine.
